- âœ… Use diagnostic tools effectively
- âœ… Interpret logs and telemetry
- âœ… Troubleshoot across component boundaries
- âœ… Optimize performance systematically
- âœ… Know when and how to escalate
- âœ… Implement preventive monitoring

